fullplot: After bringing democracy to his country, President Mohamed Nasheed of the Maldives, the lowest-lying country in the world, takes up the fight to keep his homeland from disappearing under the sea.

tomatoes.consensus: An eye-opening and appealing documentary about an earnest politician up against the closed door drama of climate change.
